== VRCA 2025 ==
The VR Community Awards for 2025 began taking nominations from December 1, to December 14, 2025. Categories were announced on November 15th. Phase one voting began January 6 through January 13, 2026. The top three nominees advance to Phase Two. Phase Two voting is held from January 20, to January 27, and the winners are revealed in the ceremony, hosted on March 15, 2026.

A few new categories were introduced: The award for Humanoid Avatar, is now separated into Male Humanoid, and Female Humanoid. The award for Furry Avatar, is now separated into Male Furry, and Female Furry. There is also a new avatar award titled "Character Avatar: The Avatar that did not take traditional forms but became a crowd favourite with its users". The award "Avatar Innovation" was removed.
